# Credentials
.env
*.env
.env.*
!.env.example
# gym.env is COMMITTED on purpose (ADR-006-A1 fail-closed contract) — fake local creds only.
# Must override *.env above so the in-repo gym guard actually ships.
!gym.env
credentials/
.kaggle/
.secrets/
*.key
*.pem

